title: Hour 2 - Mike Florio, Rodney Harrison, MLB Asterisks
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Mike Florio, Rodney Harrison, MLB Asterisks
description:
Dan talks to NFL insider Mike Florio and former NFL safety Rodney Harrison about Miami Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa's injuries from his last two games. And Dan reminds us that even Babe Ruth and Roger Maris can have asterisks next to their records, if for different reasons than Barry Bonds.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
